 launchable and new content along with fixes are added all the time. The potential of this game is pretty much limitless and if done correctly this game has the potential to be a very good game for many years to come.Keep in mind tho, game will be F2P, what this means for server cost vs income per player is to early to tell, but thers no doubt that as I predicted some years back, F2P game are here to stay. But they also bring with them new challenges and in my eyes there havent been that many ""successfull"" F2P games, atleast which did apply to me.Looking at the current state, my best guess is that the game is about a year away from releasing."
